_sText:
I made this map because i had to learn to make Maps just with Standart Content. I couldnt do his so I included just 2 custom Textures and 2 Custom Sounds.
Special gimmics are:
If 1 Team won the Round a cool screeneffect is Played.
If 1 Team won the Round customSounds are played.
I did not used Mods for theese Special Effects. 
I included all Custom Stuff in the bsp File.

Have Fun
